If you have a problem using one of the restrooms because of a customer refusing you access because of your gender identity please go to a register and ask for the MIC or for someone in the building to call Jessie. Jessie is a manger who works there and will fight for your rights to use the effing bathroom.

To get to the other head to your right from the front door and go straight back. This bathroom door is behind a privacy screen but is available for everyone to use. Both are single stall unisex and contain baby tables.
comment: Everything is inexpensive and good so if you need a safe space to stay you can sit in the back for as long as you need.
